title: Chevy Woods Previews Upcoming Wiz Khalifa Song That Sounds Pretty Fire
text:
Home > Music > Chevy Woods Previews Upcoming Wiz Khalifa Song That Sounds Pretty Fire Chevy Woods Previews Upcoming Wiz Khalifa Song That Sounds Pretty Fire 0 0 Posted by Kevin Goddard , Jan 5, 2017 at 11:44pm Wiz Khalifa has some new heat coming in 2017. 
It’s no secret that Wiz Khalifa has an upcoming project or maybe even two coming for us in 2017, but if what Chevy Woods just shared on IG last night is any indication of what’s in stored then we’re in for a real treat. 
In the scary hours of Thursday morning, the T.G.O.D rapper shared a clip of him & Wiz in the studio listening to an upcoming Wiz record, and its sounds pretty fire. In it, we here Wiz rap about being with some gangsters (referring to his TGOD crew), but not before he opens up with some bars, rapping..“I got different flavors, different strokes for different folks/ Talkin ‘bout paper, Im getting the most.” 
Unfortunately, Chevy didn’t give us much information as for the record itself or where it will live on, but that’s what helps build anticipation. Check out the preview (below) and let us know what you think in the comments.
